"{\"uid\": \"hartenergy.com-exclusives-pitts-us-qatar-face-lng-olympics-209034\", \"text\": \"In the LNG exporting space, the U.S. is squaring off with its fiercest competitor, Qatar, with both countries expected to outpace Australia. (Source: Shutterstock.com)  CEO Doug Lawler said Continental Resources is continuing its international shale foray with a second overseas investment-this time in the Vaca Muerta-following a March joint venture deal for shale exploration in Turkey.\"}"